        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Protect American Widows Act of 2024 or the PAW Act of 2024</strong></p><p>This bill redefines <em>surviving spouse</em> for purposes of the applicable filing status of such individuals. It expands from two to five years amount of time a spouse must survive a deceased spouse in order to qualify for joint filing status as a married taxpayer.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
